-- Wockhardt Advances in Mumbai After Hospitals Unit Announces Expansion Plan
-- B y   S u r e s h   S e s h a d r i
-- 2010-10-25T03:55:54Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-25/wockhardt-advances-in-mumbai-after-hospitals-unit-announces-expansion-plan.html
Wockhardt Ltd. rose in Mumbai
trading after the drugmaker said its unit plans to start a 340-
bed specialty hospital in southern Mumbai by 2012.  The shares rose 1.9 percent to 314.20 rupees as of 9:25
a.m. local time.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
